long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Turn your browser's new tab into an amazing timeline of your life! "Weeks of Life" shows you your whole life broken down into weeks, like tiny boxes on a calendar. You can see how many weeks you've already lived and how many you might have in the future.

This cool tool helps you understand just how special and important time really is. Every time you open a new tab, you'll be reminded to make the most of each day. It's super easy to use and looks really neat - kind of like a simple but beautiful chart that tells the story of your life.

Think of it as a friendly reminder to spend your time doing things that matter to you. After all, every week is a chance to do something awesome!
